matrix: none -> MenuBarPopoverView shows SetupWizard because isSetupComplete is false even if ChatGPT absent
matrix: claude-only -> UsagePopoverView shown, Claude section when usageData exists, header says Claude Usage
matrix: chatgpt-only -> AppModel refresh loop can run with hasChatGPTSessionCookie, but popover gate remains isSetupComplete-only so setup wizard is shown
matrix: both -> UsagePopoverView shown, Claude and ChatGPT sections render when both data objects exist and ChatGPT setting enabled
matrix: loading -> single Loading usage data copy when no usage data/error; refresh spinner keyed only to isRefreshing not isRefreshingChatGPT
matrix: error -> Claude top banner from errorMessage; ChatGPT inline banner from chatGPTErrorMessage when setting enabled
